'''Fjarðarheiðargöng''', also known as ''Seyðisfjarðargöng'', is a proposed<ref>[http://www.vegagerdin.is/framkvaemdir/utbod/nidurstodur-utboda/nr/15215 Vegagerðin - Rannsóknarboranir 2016]</ref> road tunnel along route 93 in [[Eastern Region (Iceland)|eastern Iceland]]. The tunnel would replace a 600m high pass between [[Seyðisfjörður]] and [[Egilsstaðir]].

